cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper deals with incremental learning in deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural networks (cs.NE). However, since the paper focuses on image classification and object detection benchmarks, it is most likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV) as these are the most relevant areas for these tasks.
